        },
        "score": 0.03205128205128205
      },
      {
        "content": "Flash-loan oracle manipulation on AMM-priced collateral\n\nDisclosure: protocol valued LP collateral using on-chain spot price; a single-transaction flash loan moved the pool, inflated collateral value, and borrowed beyond solvency. External price dependency without manipulation resistance. Mitigation: TWAP/fair-value LP pricing, deviation checks, and per-block borrow caps.",
